headline.main: SEVERAL AMERICANS RELEASED IN FRANCE; Dr. Jackson of Hospital at Neuilly Is Among Those Freed

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Oct. 2 (UP) -- Several of the 1,400 Americans arrested in occupied France have been released after examination by German authorities.
abstract: Dr S W Jackson, C Knight and Mrs C Bedaux among those released
